## Enemies

| ID | Name | HP | Speed | Reward |
|----|------|----|-------|--------|
| `basic` | Basic | 60 | 2.5/s | 5g |
| `fast` | Fast | 35 | 5.0/s | 8g |
| `tank` | Tank | 220 | 1.5/s | 15g |
| `boss` | Boss | 600 | 1.2/s | 50g |

HP scales +15% per wave: `hp × (1 + waveIndex × 0.15)`.

---

## Economy

- Start: 150 gold, 20 lives
- Wave bonus: +25 gold at end of each wave
- No upgrades, no interest (planned for later)

---

## Game Phases

```
Idle → Build (5s) → Wave → WaveClear (3s) → Build → … → Victory
                                                         ↓
                                                      GameOver (lives = 0)
```

---

## UI Panels

| Panel | Phase | Content | Status |
|-------|-------|---------|--------|
| **HUD** | Always | Gold, Lives, Wave `N / 10` | Planned |
| **Tower Shop** | Build + Wave | Horizontal scrollable bar at bottom with purchasable towers | ✅ Implemented |
| **Wave Banner** | Build → Wave transition | "Wave N" flash, then fades | Planned |
| **Game Over** | GameOver | "DEFEAT" + retry button | Planned |
| **Victory** | Victory | "VICTORY" + score/restart button | Planned |

### Tower Shop UI
- Location: `UI/TowerShop.xaml`
- Component: `Scripts/Components/TowerShopHud.ts`
- Attached to: `player.hstf` (TowerShopUI entity with CustomUiComponent)
- Type: ScreenSpace (mobile)
- Features:
  - ~100px tall bar docked to bottom
  - Horizontal scrollable list of tower buttons
  - Each button shows tower name and cost with gold icon
  - Visual states: affordable (full opacity) / too_expensive (greyed out, 0.5 opacity)
  - Tap fires `towerTap` event with tower ID

### ViewModel bindings
```typescript
// TowerShopViewModel
items: readonly TowerShopItemViewModel[]  // tower list
selectedTowerId: string                    // currently selected tower

// TowerShopItemViewModel (per tower)
iconPath: string
name: string
cost: number
state: string      // "affordable" | "too_expensive"
towerId: string
```

---

## Events Reference

| Event | Payload | Used by |
|-------|---------|---------|
| `GamePhaseChanged` | `phase: GamePhase` | HUD, WaveBanner |
| `ResourceChanged` | `gold, lives` | HUD |
| `WaveStarted` | `waveIndex, totalWaves` | HUD, WaveBanner |
| `WaveCompleted` | `waveIndex` | HUD |
| `GridTapped` | `col, row` | TowerService |
| `InitTower` | `defId, col, row` | TowerController |
| `InitEnemy` | `defId` | EnemyController |
| `InitProjectile` | `targetEnemyId, damage, speed, props` | ProjectileController |
| `TakeDamage` | `damage, debuffs[]` | EnemyController |
| `EnemyDied` | `enemyId, reward` | — |
| `EnemyReachedEnd` | `enemyId` | GameManager |
| `TowerShopSelected` | `towerId: string` | TowerShopHud |
| `GameOver` | `won: boolean` | UI |
